OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FMeningitis B vaccines will be offered
OL,7,Fto some Year 11 school pupils affected
OL,8,Fby the outbreak in Kent, health
OL,9,Fofficials have said.
OL,11,FThe development comes as new figures
OL,12,Ffrom the UK Health Security Agency
OL,13,F(UKHSA) show the number of cases of
OL,14,Fmeningitis have fallen.
OL,16,FTwenty cases were confirmed, as of
OL,17,F12.30pm on Monday, with a further
OL,18,Fthree under investigation, bringing
OL,19,Fthe total to 23.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
