FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FThat figure was down from 29 on
OL,7,FSunday, when 20 cases were confirmed
OL,8,Fand a further nine were under
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FOfficials started vaccinating
OL,12,FUniversity of Kent students on
OL,13,FWednesday March 18.
OL,15,FThe following day, on a visit to the
OL,16,Fcampus, Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,17,Fsaid the programme would be expanded
OL,18,Fto more people, including sixth form
OL,19,Fpupils at four schools with known or
OL,20,Fsuspected cases of meningitis B.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FMinisters have now agreed to offer
OL,7,Fjabs to Year 11 pupils at these
OL,8,Fschools, the UKHSA said.
OL,10,FOfficials said widening the programme
OL,11,Fis a precautionary measure to ensure
OL,12,Flonger-term protection. Further
OL,13,Fdetails on the outbreak have also been
OL,14,Fpublished by the UKHSA.
OL,16,FThe cases have a median age of 19, and
OL,17,Fwhile the majority are in education,
OL,18,Ffive are not students.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
