PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FMost patients (87%) attended Club
OL,7,FChemistry, in Canterbury, at least
OL,8,Fonce between March 5 and 7 before
OL,9,Fbecoming unwell.
OL,11,FMost of those were students, and the
OL,12,Fthree cases who did not go to the
OL,13,Fnightclub are all University of Kent
OL,14,Fstudents living in halls with links to
OL,15,Fthose who did attend.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
