FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FOfficials also revealed the earliest
OL,7,Fknown case became unwell on March 9,
OL,8,Fand the latest on March 16. Meanwhile,
OL,9,Fthe peak of the outbreak was on March
OL,10,F13, according to the UKHSA
OL,12,FAnalysis by the agency has shown the
OL,13,Fstrain that caused the outbreak in
OL,14,FKent does respond to antibiotics and
OL,15,Fthe meningitis B vaccine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
