OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FProfessor Robin May, chief scientific
OL,7,Fofficer at UKHSA, said: "This
OL,8,Fpreliminary analysis offers strong
OL,9,Freassurance that our existing
OL,10,Fvaccinations and antibiotic treatment
OL,11,Foffer will be effective against this
OL,12,Fstrain.
OL,14,F"In collaboration with the research
OL,15,Fcommunity, we will continue intensive
OL,16,Flaboratory investigations of the
OL,17,Fstrain to determine how the spread of
OL,18,Fthe outbreak may have been influenced
OL,19,Fby the bacterial strain, social or
OL,20,Fenvironmental conditions, and
OL,21,Fpopulation immunity."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
