PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774368667
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be offered to
OL,4,Csome Year 11 pupils in Kent
OL,6,FAll patients in the Kent outbreak have
OL,7,Frequired hospital admission. Nine were
OL,8,Fadmitted to the intensive care unit,
OL,9,Fwhere four remain.
OL,11,FThe two students who have died are 18-
OL,12,Fyear-old Juliette Kenny, who was
OL,13,Fdescribed by her family as "fit,
OL,14,Fhealthy and strong" before her death,
OL,15,Fand a University of Kent student.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
